<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>bạsmk yạ rb tjmʿnạ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- biạs̊mika yā rabũ taj̊maʿunā
 ḥaẘla sẖakẖ̊ṣika biạl̊ḥubĩ ạlnãqī̃
 hakadẖā naf̊raḥu maʿaⁿạ hunā
 nudẖīʿu maẘtaka ḥatãy̱ tajī

[V2]
 2- ḥaẘlaka yā rabũ kanīsatuk̊
 tas̊judu ḥatãy̱ ạllĩqāʾi ạl̊qarīb̊
 nā̊̉kulu ạl̊kẖub̊za wanasẖ̊rabu ạl̊kā̊̉s̊
 kaẙ nadẖ̊kura ḥubãka yā ḥabīb̊

[V3]
 3- fī ḥuḍūrika ạl̊qal̊bu yaf̊raḥu
 wanas̊judu biḥurĩyãẗi ạlrũwḥ̊
 waḥaẘlaka naḥ̊nu nusabĩḥu
 laka ạảyũhā ạl̊kẖarūfu ạl̊madẖ̊būḥ̊

[V4]
 4- wakam̊ takūnu ạảf̊rāḥu ạl̊ḥuḍūr̊
 min̊ ḥaẘlika fī ạl̊baẙti ạlạảbadī̃
 yā laʿuẓ̊mi ạl̊hanāʾi wālsũrūr̊
 lil̊kanīsaẗi maʿ̊ka fī ạl̊maj̊di</lyrics>
</song>